<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Video Unavailable</title>
    <style>
         @import url('https://p.poketube.fun/https://fonts.bunny.net/css?family=roboto:400,500&display=swap');

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #000000;  
            color: #f1f1f1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        #error-container {
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .error-icon {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            fill: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 400;  
            margin: 0 0 12px 0;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #aaaaaa;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .might-be {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #f1f1f1;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .reasons-list {
            text-align: left;
            display: inline-block;  
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0 auto 36px auto;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #aaaaaa;
            line-height: 1.6;
            list-style-type: none; 
        }

        .reasons-list li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 18px;
        }

        .reasons-list li:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

         .reasons-list li::before {
            content: "•";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #717171; 
        }

        a {
            color: #3ea6ff;  
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .btn-home {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            color: #0f0f0f;
            border: none;
            padding: 9px 16px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-radius: 18px; 
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.2s, opacity 0.2s;
            font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            background-color: #d9d9d9;
        }

        .btn-home:active {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .report-issue {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #717171;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .report-issue a {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #aaaaaa; 
        }
        
        .report-issue a:hover {
            color: #f1f1f1;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="error-container">
        
        <svg class="error-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v6z"/>
        </svg>

        <h1>Video unavailable</h1>
        
        <p class="subtitle">
            This video isn't available any more. (╥﹏╥)
        </p>

        <div class="might-be">This usually happens because...</div>

        <ul class="reasons-list">
            <li>The video was removed by the uploader.</li>
            <li>The uploader closed their account.</li>
            <li>The video was taken down for Terms of Service violations.</li>
            <li>The video ID provided is invalid.</li>
        </ul>

        <div>
            <button class="btn-home" onclick="window.location.href='/';">
                Go Home
            </button>
        </div>

        <div class="report-issue">
            Think this is a Poke mistake?<br>
            <a href="https://codeberg.org/ashleyirispuppy/poke/issues/new/choose" target="_blank">Report an issue here</a>.
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>